/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88a78e8cababef47d1d8963258c38ff90d423cf8","tid":303670,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T14:07:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 吹奏移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但又冇哂方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n根本台灣想食堆香港啲人材</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講真，香港人有一樣野，<br />\n普遍台灣人都冇：<br />\n<br />\n轉數快，又適應到唔同環境。<br />\n<br />\n不過，我覺得現任總統做得有些鬼&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n似乎下屆做唔成機會都幾高。"},{"pid":"4c9d94cd40acd7525fb1bc72841b5a79ada3802a","tid":303670,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T14:07:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去台灣等於嘥錢<br />\n去其他地方好過</blockquote><br />\n如果香港個金融中心地位死左<br />\n估下邊個地方會係2nd choice</blockquote><br />\n係都新加坡先啦幾時輪到佢台灣咩</blockquote><br />\n一語中的</blockquote><br />\n係輪到好多地方都未到台灣。"},{"pid":"8d0c437c85e83b0b43da29afe6858bc61d29a99f","tid":303670,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T14:09:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去台灣等於嘥錢<br />\n去其他地方好過</blockquote><br />\n如果香港個金融中心地位死左<br />\n估下邊個地方會係2nd choice</blockquote><br />\n一定唔會係台灣先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7622b6622dc5e821e8677e4f318a6d3222e86a21","tid":303670,"uid":54684,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T14:12:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果台灣係大膽一D<br />\n其實台灣可以自己搞一個特別行政區<br />\n<br />\n畀香港人移民過去<br />\n用哂香港既法律 + 制度<br />\n所有金融文化，都可以搬過去<br />\n再切實畀當地自治<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新香港就要繳稅畀台灣<br />\n用GDP加一個百份比<br />\n<br />\n咁可以做到東亞區既金融中心<br />\n少好多政治上既問題/威脅<br />\n台灣自己又可以收錢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老實講，唔係無得諗<br />\n係睇有無膽去做