擇既<br />\n始終港人都會易適應d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁不如移日本搏佢谷底反彈<br />\n反正都好難融入,要真正融入都係要自己係果邊土生土長既後代先會有可能<br />\n唔係以為大家都寫繁中,語言溝通冇太大問題就以為容易適應掛?<br />\n往往最大難關都係文化,思想同價值觀,呢三點可以apply 落任何國家度"},{"pid":"aae5567b3e2efe3438d8e22082a5aeb14ca45e0b","tid":303670,"uid":3112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T19:07:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 吹奏移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但又冇哂方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n根本台灣想食堆香港啲人材</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n人才要走唔會揀台灣啦<br />\n如意算盤打唔響</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我懷疑佢地LOCAL 企業究竟比唔比得起個salary 請香港D人才過去"},{"pid":"5281bc995a1c1854ca98962c88e9b877c23d9a15","tid":303670,"uid":3112,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T19:13:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我好撚羨慕日本人對臺灣人咁好咁友善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去黑門巿場大大隻字多謝台灣人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明我都有捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港集氣捐到有當年台灣人捐咁多既話,佢地實對你好好+好友善架<br />\n<br />\n中國同英國政府deal億億聲既contract,,直頭可以請埋事頭婆出黎食飯+響N門禮砲tim<br />\n<br />\n一切都係錢既問題<br />\n<br />\n但係現實你望下受災區,個復修工作進度都好麻麻地<br />\n<br />\n咁究竟D捐款用左係邊? 根本冇人知"},{"pid":"7bfde10936dd7f5d8fee878409147e71786cf043","tid":303670,"uid":54629,"like":0,"di