唔到D咩錢,假如兩邊都冇樓痴屋企人住,咁香港打工可以用黎儲蓄既錢一定多過台灣,因為香港人工高太多,最多一開始可能差唔多,但係三五七年後一定有明顯差距</blockquote><br />\n有工業點都好過冇<br />\n香港冇晒工業咁滯比人鍊住春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n除咗英文好過佢哋一般人外(起碼簡單E-mail/對話搞得掂)<br />\n普通香港人有咩優勢同搵到咩工？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔講專業人士<br />\n佢哋去邊都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59b618ba56e8da007af8ab11661da7ad2fece183","tid":303670,"uid":115197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T19:46:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 吹奏移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但又冇哂方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n根本台灣想食堆香港啲人材</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n現成高效率英語高業人材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一本passport換你香港政府幾十年既人材投資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"050804e4c84fbd2b9e77fab982504c3182959b82","tid":303670,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T23:00:18.000Z","msg":"老老柒柒，有無方法唔服兵役<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}